## Wrong vs right

| Wrong | Right |
|---|---|
| `BMad — Sprint Status (2026-06-19)` | `BMad — Sprint Status` |
| `BMad — Quick Dev : Disabled Controls Look` | `BMad — Quick Dev : Look contrôles inactifs` |
| `BMad — Correct Course : Réduction de la latence audio` | `BMad — Correct Course : Latence audio` |
| Two chats both named `BMad — Quick Dev : Look contrôles inactifs` | Second becomes `BMad — Quick Dev : Look contrôles inactifs (1)` |
